#

Vegetable Sambar

$10.5
250 kcal

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

IndianStewVeganSpicyComfort Food

Description

A hearty and flavorful South Indian stew made with lentils and mixed vegetables, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • Toor dal (pigeon peas): 1 cup
  • Mixed vegetables (carrots, beans, potatoes): 2 cups
  • Tomato: 1 large, chopped
  • Tamarind paste: 2 tablespoons
  • Sambar powder: 2 tablespoons
  • Mustard seeds: 1 teaspoon
  • Curry leaves: 10 leaves
  • Turmeric powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Water: 4 cups
  • Cilantro (for garnish): 2 tablespoons, chopped
